**Root cause: AP-070** (framer-motion inline `transform` overwrites CSS class transform — originally the placement transform was on the `motion.span`, not the parent div). The two-element split was correctly applied to the JSX, but the SCSS `.highlightLabelAnchor` is missing `width: max-content`, which is what makes `translate(-100%)` mean "label text width" rather than "viewport width minus left".

