>
> **AP-069 corollary — `will-change` on a `mix-blend-mode` element creates the same isolation failure as `position: fixed`.** `will-change` on any property promotes the element to a compositor layer with an isolated stacking context. `mix-blend-mode` in an isolated context blends against the layer's own empty background. Keep `will-change` only on the inner animated span, never on the blend-mode anchor.
